{"word":"G5274 - ὑπολαμβάνω - hypolambánō - hoop-ol-am-ban'-o - Answer","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπολαμβάνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypolambánō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-ol-am-ban'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Answer</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நினை, பதில் சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. to take up in order to raise, to bear on high, to take up and carry away"},{"paragraph":"2. to receive hospitably, welcome"},{"paragraph":"3. to take up, follow in speech"},{"paragraph":"4. to take up in the mind, to assume, suppose"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G2983 - λαμβάνω - lambánō - lam-ban'-o/2983\">G2983</a>; to <i>take</i> from <i>below</i>, that is, <i>carry upward</i>; figuratively to <i>take up</i>, that is, <i>continue</i> a discourse or topic; mentally to <i>assume</i> (<i>presume</i>): - answer, receive, suppose.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1949/1949\">G1949</a>, <a href=\"#/G2638/2638\">G2638</a>, <a href=\"#/G2983/2983\">G2983</a>, <a href=\"#/G3335/3335\">G3335</a>, <a href=\"#/G3336/3336\">G3336</a>, <a href=\"#/G353/353\">G353</a>, <a href=\"#/G354/354\">G354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3880/3880\">G3880</a>, <a href=\"#/G423/423\">G423</a>, <a href=\"#/G4301/4301\">G4301</a>, <a href=\"#/G4355/4355\">G4355</a>, <a href=\"#/G4356/4356\">G4356</a>, <a href=\"#/G5274/5274\">G5274</a>"}]}